OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FAn organised criminal operation that
OL,8,Fsaw hundreds of tonnes of household
OL,9,Fand commercial waste illegally dumped
OL,10,Fand buried across Hampshire and
OL,11,FCambridgeshire has been busted, thanks
OL,12,Fto a dashcam belonging to one of the
OL,13,Fcriminals.
OL,15,FSeven men have been sentenced at
OL,16,FWinchester Crown Court following a
OL,17,Fsuccessful prosecution by the
OL,18,FEnvironment Agency.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
