FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FOn the morning of 31 July 2019, a
OL,8,Fconvoy of lorries arrived at
OL,9,FKingsclere Lime Quarry near Tadley,
OL,10,FHampshire, and dumped approximately
OL,11,F200 tonnes of shredded household and
OL,12,Fcommercial waste.
OL,14,FThe owners of the quarry had given no
OL,15,Fpermission for their land to be used
OL,16,Fas a rubbish dump.
OL,18,FWATCH: The moment a lorry enters the
OL,19,Fillegal waste site, captured by a
OL,20,Fdefendant's own dashcam.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FHampshire Police and Environment
OL,8,FAgency officers were called to the
OL,9,Fquarry after receiving reports of the
OL,10,Fillegal activity.
OL,12,FOnce there, they seized crucial
OL,13,Fdashcam footage from a lorry belonging
OL,14,Fto defendant Peter Elliott.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThis footage not only captured the
OL,8,Fillegal activities in Hampshire, but
OL,9,Fit also led investigators directly to
OL,10,Fa second, previously unknown dump site
OL,11,Fin Farcet, Cambridgeshire, where
OL,12,Fhundreds of tonnes of waste had been
OL,13,Fburied in the preceding days.
OL,15,FWithout the seized dashcam footage,
OL,16,Fofficials say no one would have known
OL,17,Fabout the scale of the environmental
OL,18,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe investigation revealed a highly
OL,8,Fcoordinated waste-crime network
OL,9,Foperating across two separate sites
OL,10,Fbetween July and August 2019:
OL,12,FThe court heard that Steven Rozario,
OL,13,Facting as the waste broker, arranged
OL,14,Ffor waste to be transported from at
OL,15,Fleast three producer sites. He used
OL,16,FBarry Wilkes's haulage firm, Wembley
OL,17,FGroup Ltd, to move the rubbish.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FRozario's company, Active Management
OL,8,FFacilities Limited, failed to meet
OL,9,Fbasic duty of care standards. Their
OL,10,Fwaste transfer notes were heavily
OL,11,Fdeficient, lacking proper destination
OL,12,Fdetails, confirmation of permits, and
OL,13,Fany proof that the waste had actually
OL,14,Freached a lawful facility.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FColin Chiverton, Area Environment
OL,8,FManager at the Environment Agency,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This was a serious, organised
OL,10,Fand brazen criminal operation that saw
OL,11,Fhundreds of tonnes of controlled waste
OL,12,Fdumped and buried at sites completely
OL,13,Funfit and unpermitted to receive it.
OL,14,FThe damage caused to those sites, and
OL,15,Fthe risk posed to the surrounding
OL,16,Fenvironment and communities, is
OL,17,Fentirely unacceptable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,F"All seven defendants had clear legal
OL,8,Fresponsibilities ` as lorry operators,
OL,9,Fsite managers, waste haulier,
OL,10,Ftransport manager and waste broker `
OL,11,Fand all seven chose to ignore them. We
OL,12,Fwill pursue those involved in waste
OL,13,Fcrime at every level of the chain,
OL,14,Ffrom drivers to brokers."
OL,16,FAll seven defendants were convicted of
OL,17,Fvarious environmental offences under
OL,18,Fthe Environmental Protection Act 1990
OL,19,F(and the Criminal Attempts Act 1981 in
OL,20,FBoaca's case).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
