PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784211519
OL,3,CCriminal's own dashcam footage
OL,4,Cuncovers massive illegal waste dumping
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe judge singled out haulage director
OL,8,FBarry Wilkes as the individual bearing
OL,9,Fthe most responsibility.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
